msgid ""
"You noticed Izra at the Wetland Stable staring\n"
"keenly into Hylia River.\n"
"\n"
"His attention was fixed on a <1.se_co>treasure chest<2.re_co> on\n"
"the bed of Hylia River, but he is at a loss as\n"
